DynamicGameObject, TileObject
public class GameObject
extends com.jme.scene.Node

GameObject Is the overhead for all objects within the application, static or dynamic. GameObject includes the location and object ID, allowing any object in any situation to be questioned and changed.

GameObject.java,v 0.1 2006/10/03
